{{#post}}

<main class="gh-main">
    <article class="gh-article {{post_class}}">

        {{#match @page.show_title_and_feature_image}}
            <header class="gh-article-header gh-canvas">
                <h1 class="gh-article-title is-title">{{title}}</h1>
                {{#if custom_excerpt}}
                    <p class="gh-article-excerpt is-body">{{custom_excerpt}}</p>
                {{/if}}
                {{> "feature-image"}}
            </header>
        {{/match}}

        <section class="gh-content gh-canvas is-body">
            {{content}}
        </section>

    </article>
</main>

{{/post}}

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            background: #002244;
            color: #ffffff;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #002244 0%, #006b7d 100%);
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-out;
        }

        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #FC4C02;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.5s both;
        }

        .header .year {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: rgba(252, 76, 2, 0.3);
            margin-top: 2rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 1s both;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .scroll-container {
            position: relative;
        }

        .sticky-visual {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: #001a33;
        }

        .visual-content {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            height: 500px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            transition: all 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        .record-display {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #FC4C02;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(252, 76, 2, 0.5);
            font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif;
        }

        .record-label {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        .stat-display {
            display: flex;
            gap: 3rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .stat-box {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: rgba(252, 76, 2, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            min-width: 150px;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #FC4C02;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .player-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .player-card {
            background: rgba(252, 76, 2, 0.1);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #FC4C02;
        }

        .player-name {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #FC4C02;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .player-position {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .trophy-icon {
            font-size: 12rem;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
            }
        }

        .content-sections {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content-step {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }

        .step-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: rgba(0, 34, 68, 0.95);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #FC4C02;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: 4rem;
        }

        .step-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #FC4C02;
        }

        .step-content p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .footer {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #006b7d 0%, #002244 100%);
        }

        .footer h2 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #FC4C02;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .header .year {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }

            .record-display {
                font-size: 5rem;
            }

            .record-label {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .step-content {
                margin-right: 2rem;
                margin-left: 2rem;
            }

            .step-content h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .step-content p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .stat-display {
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .stat-number {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .trophy-icon {
                font-size: 8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{title}}</h1>
        {{#if custom_excerpt}}
            <p class="subtitle">{{custom_excerpt}}</p>
        {{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="scroll-container">
        <div class="sticky-visual">
            <div class="visual-content" id="visualContent">
                <div class="record-display">17-0</div>
                <div class="record-label">Perfect Record</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-sections">
            <div class="content-step" data-step="0">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>A Season Like No Other</h2>
                    <p>In 1972, the Miami Dolphins accomplished what no NFL team had done before, and what no team has done since. They finished the season without a single loss, going 17-0 including the playoffs and Super Bowl.</p>
                    {{content}}
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-step" data-step="1">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>The Coach</h2>
                    <p>Don Shula, in just his third season with Miami, orchestrated one of the greatest coaching performances in sports history. His no-nonsense approach and innovative strategies transformed the Dolphins into an unstoppable force.</p>
                    {{content}}
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-step" data-step="2">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>The Perfect Pair</h2>
                    <p>When starting quarterback Bob Griese was injured in Week 5, backup Earl Morrall stepped in seamlessly. The duo combined for 19 touchdowns and led the team without missing a beat, showcasing the depth that made this team special.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-step" data-step="3">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>The No-Name Defense</h2>
                    <p>Miami's defense earned the nickname "No-Name Defense" because of their lack of star power. But they were dominant, allowing just 12.2 points per game and creating turnovers when it mattered most.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-step" data-step="4">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>The Ground Game</h2>
                    <p>Larry Csonka and Mercury Morris formed a devastating running back duo, each rushing for over 1,000 yards. Their punishing style wore down defenses and controlled the clock, making Miami nearly impossible to beat.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-step" data-step="5">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>Super Bowl VII</h2>
                    <p>On January 14, 1973, at the Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum, the Dolphins defeated the Washington Redskins 14-7 to complete their perfect season. Safety Jake Scott's two interceptions earned him Super Bowl MVP honors.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-step" data-step="6">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <h2>The Legacy</h2>
                    <p>Over 50 years later, the 1972 Dolphins remain the only team to complete a perfect season in NFL history. Team members famously toast champagne each year when the last undefeated team loses, celebrating their unique achievement.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <h2>Still Perfect</h2>
        <p>The 1972 Miami Dolphins proved that teamwork, discipline, and determination can create something truly extraordinary. Their 17-0 record stands as a testament to one of the greatest teams in sports history.</p>
